  <steps>
    <step num="0">Preheat the oven to 300˚F (150˚C). </step>
    <step num="1">In a large bowl, combine the walnuts, egg whites, sugar, and salt and mix with a rubber spatula until the walnuts are well-coated. </step>
    <step num="2">Spread the walnut mixture evenly on a parchment paper-lined baking sheet. </step>
    <step num="3">Bake for 30-40 minutes, stirring every 10 minutes, until the walnuts are crystallized. </step>
    <step num="4">Cool completely. </step>
    <step num="5">Enjoy! </step>
  </steps>
